msgid "While modeling a scene with blender, certain objects can be marked to participate in the fluid simulation, e.g. as fluid or as an obstacle. The bounding box of another object will be used to define a box-shaped region to simulate the fluid in (the so called \"simulation domain\"). The global simulation parameters (such as viscosity and gravity) can be set for this domain object."
